import '../style/table.css' import Tbody from "./Tbody"; import 'flowbite'; import Search from "./Search"; import {useState} from "react"; import events from './eventsData' import Sort from "./Sort"; const Table = () => { const [filteredData, setFilteredData] = useState(events); const handleSearch = (searchKey, searchInput) => { if (!searchKey.trim() || !searchInput.trim()) { setFilteredData(events); return; } if (searchKey === 'Title') { searchKey = 'name' } else if (searchKey === "Location") { searchKey = 'place' } else { searchKey = searchKey.toLowerCase(); } const filtered = events.filter(item => item[searchKey].toLowerCase().includes(searchInput.toLowerCase())); setFilteredData(filtered); }; const handleSort = (sortKey) => { if (sortKey !== 'Deadline') { console.log(filteredData) const sortedData = [...filteredData].sort((a, b) => a[sortKey].localeCompare(b[sortKey])); setFilteredData(sortedData); } } const styles = { position: 'absolute', inset: 'auto auto 0px 0px', margin: '0px', transform: 'translate3d(522.5px, 3847.5px, 0px)', }; return (
